msgctxt "56_Barkeep"
msgid "Oh, Chigusa-san."
msgstr "Oh, Chigusa."

msgctxt "68_Chigusa"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "80_Barkeep"
msgid "Please, take a seat."
msgstr "Por favor, tome asiento."

msgctxt "152_Kiryu"
msgid "Hold on. Didn't you say this seat was reserved?"
msgstr "Un momento. ¿No dijiste que este asiento estaba reservado?"

msgctxt "164_Barkeep"
msgid "That's right. For Chigusa's boyfriend, Yusaku-kun."
msgstr "Claro. Para el novio de Chigusa, Yusaku."

msgctxt "176_Kiryu"
msgid "And the drink?"
msgstr "¿Y la bebida?"

msgctxt "188_Barkeep"
msgid "It's for him as well. Yusaku-kun would always sit in that\\r\n"
"very seat when he came here to take a load off."
msgstr "También para el. Yusaku siempre se sentaba en ese mismo\\r\n"
"asiento cuando venía aquí a relajarse."

msgctxt "200_Barkeep"
msgid "Today makes it a year since he passed. Even still, I had a\\r\n"
"feeling he would come in for a drink today."
msgstr "Hoy marca un año desde que falleció. Aun así, tenía la\\r \n"
"sensación que vendría a tomar algo hoy."

msgctxt "212_Kiryu"
msgid "So he's really gone..."
msgstr "Así que realmente se ha ido..."

msgctxt "224_Barkeep"
msgid "He was so young, too. That's the scary thing about cancer.\\r\n"
"Sometimes it spreads so fast, it'll be far too late for\\r\n"
"treatment by the time you even know it's there."
msgstr "Era tan joven. Eso es lo aterrador del cáncer.\\r\n"
"Hay veces que se extiende tan rápido que será\\r\n"
"demasiado tarde para el tratamiento una vez lo encuentren."

msgctxt "236_Barkeep"
msgid "Chigusa-san knows what happened... but she can't seem to\\r\n"
"bring herself to believe Yusaku-kun is gone."
msgstr "Chigusa sabe lo que ha pasado... pero no puede hacerse\\r\n"
"a la idea de que Yusaku ya no está."

msgctxt "248_Barkeep"
msgid "He had a bad habit of lying to her, so she convinced herself\\r\n"
"that his death was just another one of his lies."
msgstr "Él tenía el mal hábito de mentirle, así que ella se\\r\n"
"autoconvenció de que su muerte era otra de sus mentiras."

msgctxt "260_Kiryu"
msgid "She convinced herself I was Yusaku-kun, too."
msgstr "Hasta se autoconvenció a si misma de que yo era Yusaku."

msgctxt "272_Barkeep"
msgid "So it seems."
msgstr "Eso parece."

msgctxt "284_Chigusa"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "296_Barkeep"
msgid "Chigusa-san... That's enough. I know it hurts to hear this,\\r\n"
"but waiting for Yusaku-kun isn't going to bring him back."
msgstr "Chigusa... ya basta. Sé que duele oír esto, pero esperar\\r\n"
"a Yusaku no va a hacer que vuelva."

msgctxt "308_Chigusa"
msgid "No. No, I don't believe it!"
msgstr "No. ¡No, no me lo creo!"

msgctxt "320_Barkeep"
msgid "Chigusa..."
msgstr "Chigusa..."

msgctxt "332_Chigusa"
msgid "Please... This is all just a stupid lie, right?"
msgstr "Por favor... Todo esto es solo una mentira estúpida, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "344_Chigusa"
msgid "He can't be dead, he just can't!"
msgstr "¡No puede estar muerto, me niego!"

msgctxt "356_Chigusa"
msgid "This engagement ring was a lie, too. He never wanted to get\\r\n"
"married. He's just running away..."
msgstr "Este anillo de compromiso también es una mentira. Nunca\\r\n"
"quiso casarse. Solo se la pasa huyendo..."

msgctxt "368_Chigusa"
msgid "After all those lies, why would he tell the truth this time!?"
msgstr "Después de todas las mentiras, ¿¡por qué diría la verdad esta vez!?"

msgctxt "380_Barkeep"
msgid "Chigusa-san... I have a letter for you from Yusaku-san.\\r\n"
"I think it's finally time for you to read it."
msgstr "Chigusa... tengo una carta de Yusaku.\\r\n"
"Creo que ya es hora de que la leas."

msgctxt "392_Chigusa"
msgid "A letter?"
msgstr "¿Una carta?"

msgctxt "404_Barkeep"
msgid "He dropped it off when he found out he didn't have much time\\r\n"
"left. Told me to give it to you long after he was gone."
msgstr "La dejó cuando descubrió que le quedaba poco tiempo.\\r\n"
"Me pidió que te la de mucho después de que se fuera."

msgctxt "416_Barkeep"
msgid "That's when he told you he was leaving town. He didn't want\\r\n"
"to burden you with his death, Chigusa-san. He wanted you to\\r\n"
"move on, fall in love again..."
msgstr "Entonces fue cuando te dijo que se iba de la ciudad. Él \\r\n"
"no quería hacerte cargar con su muerte, Chigusa. Quería\\r\n"
"que pasaras página, que te enamoraras de nuevo..."

msgctxt "428_Barkeep"
msgid "And he knew that you'd probably think this was just another\\r\n"
"one of his lies."
msgstr "Y sabía que pensarías que era otra\\r \n"
"de sus mentiras."

msgctxt "440_Barkeep"
msgid "He said that part with a little smile. I can remember it clear as day."
msgstr "Eso último lo dijo con una pequeña sonrisa. Lo recuerdo \\r\n"
"como si fuera ayer."

msgctxt "452_Chigusa"
msgid "Why didn't he tell me? He only had a few months left, and we\\r\n"
"didn't even get to spend that time together. I wish I could\\r\n"
"have been there to support him..."
msgstr "¿Por qué no me dijo nada? Solo le quedaban unos meses,\\r\n"
"y ni siqueira pudimos pasarlos juntos. Ojalá hubiera\\r\n"
"podido estar ahí para apoyarle..."

msgctxt "464_Chigusa"
msgid "Yusaku... I miss you so much..."
msgstr "Yusaku... te echo tanto de menos..."

msgctxt "476_Kiryu"
msgid "Chigusa..."
msgstr "Chigusa..."

msgctxt "488_Chigusa"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "500_Kiryu"
msgid "Are you crying?"
msgstr "¿Estás llorando?"

msgctxt "512_Chigusa"
msgid "No, of course not. *sniffle*"
msgstr "No, claro que no. *solloza*"

msgctxt "524_Chigusa"
msgid "I would never cry over an idiot like that. I was just faking\\r\n"
"it. Lying, like he always did to me."
msgstr "Nunca lloraría por un idiota como él. Estaba\\r\n"
"fingiendo. Mentía, como él siempre me mentía a mi."

msgctxt "536_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "548_Chigusa"
msgid "Please, I'm fine. You don't have to worry about me anymore."
msgstr "Por favor, estoy bien. Ya no hace falta que se preocupen por mí."

msgctxt "560_Kiryu"
msgid "Chigusa, there's no point hiding it. You can put on a brave\\r\n"
"face all you want, but I know you're hurting deep down."
msgstr "Chigusa, no es necesario esconderlo. Puedes poner la mejor\\r\n"
"cara que tengas, pero sé que en el fondo te duele."

msgctxt "572_Chigusa"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "584_Kiryu"
msgid "And think about it."
msgstr "Y piénsalo bien."

msgctxt "596_Kiryu"
msgid "Yusaku lied to you so you'd be happy. He knew he was dying,\\r\n"
"but told you one last lie to get you to move on and smile."
msgstr "Yusaku te mintió para que estuvieras contenta. Él sabía\\r \n"
"que se estaba muriendo, y te mintió una última vez así \\r\n"
"pasabas página y sonreías."

msgctxt "608_Kiryu"
msgid "So if you're going to lie and say you're fine, the least you\\r\n"
"can do is smile while you say it. For Yusaku."
msgstr "Así que si vas a mentir y decir que estás bien, lo mínimo\\r\n"
"que podrías hacer es sonreír mientras lo dices. Por Yusaku."

msgctxt "620_Chigusa"
msgid "I'm not fine... *sob*"
msgstr "No estoy bien... *solloza*"

msgctxt "632_Kiryu"
msgid "And that's okay. It's all right to cry, Chigusa. If you ask\\r\n"
"me, I don't think Yusaku would have wanted you to hide how\\r\n"
"you really feel."
msgstr "Y está bien. No pasa nada por llorar, Chigusa. En mi\\r\n"
"opinión, no creo que Yusaku hubiese querido que\\r\n"
"escondieras tus sentimientos."

msgctxt "644_Chigusa"
msgid "Yusaku... Yusaku! *sob*"
msgstr "¡Yusaku... Yusaku! *solloza*"

msgctxt "656_Kiryu"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

